  "text": "After the pre-processing procedure described above, Xtail takes in raw read counts of RPF and mRNA, and performs median-of-ratios normalization [CITATION_1] by default. Alternatively, users can choose to provide normalized read counts and skip the built-in normalization in Xtail.",
